-- Harvard Endowment Portfolio Expands 11%, Ends Fiscal 2010 at $27.6 Billion
-- B y   J o A n n e   N o r t o n
-- 2010-10-20T14:09:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/harvard-endowment-portfolio-expands-11-ends-fiscal-2010-at-27-6-billion.html
Harvard University’s endowment
portfolio was $27.6 billion on June 30, the end of fiscal 2010,
President Drew Gilpin Faust said in the university’s annual
financial report.  The report, issued Oct. 15, noted that Harvard’s endowment
portfolio had a return of 11 percent for the year.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
JoAnne Norton at 
 jnorton@bloomberg.net  